hate%20crime%2C%20the%20RPF%20has%20dismissed%20two%20more%20constables%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfailing%20to%20discharge%20their%20duties%E2%80%9D.%20Chaudhary%20was%20caught%20on%20camera%20hurling%20abuses%20at%20passengers%20from%20Muslim%20communities%20and%20gunning%20them%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaudhary%20was%20immediately%20arrested%20and%2C%20following%20uproar%20on%20social%20media%20and%20by%20several%20rights%20activists%20and%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20he%20was%20booked%20under%20appropriate%20sections%20for%20murder%20and%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20two%20communities.%20Now%2C%20two%20of%20his%20colleagues%20%E2%80%93%20Amay%20Acharya%20and%20Narendra%20Parmar%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20dismissed%20for%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20protect%20three%20passengers%20(Abdul%20Kadar%20Mohamed%20Hussain%20Bhanpurawala%2C%20Syed%20Saifuddin%20and%20Asgar%20Abbas%20Sheikh)%20and%20RPF%20Assistant%20Sub-Inspector%20Tikaram%20Meena.%20All%20four%20were%20gunned%20down%20inside%20the%20Jaipur-Mumbai%20Central%20Superfast%20Express%20on%20July%2031%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dismissal%20order%2C%20as%20reported%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2F2-more-rpf-cops-dismissed-in-train-hate-killings-failed-to-discharge-duty-9205487%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20mentions%20specific%20reasons%20for%20their%20dismissal.%20The%20dismissal%20orders%20read%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20accused%20constables%20on%20duty%20to%20provide%20security%20and%20protection%20to%20the%20passengers%E2%80%A6%20They%2C%20however%2C%20failed%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20The%20act%20of%20the%20accused%20constables%20would%20erode%20trust%20among%20passengers%20towards%20RPF%20and%E2%80%A6%20send%20a%20wrong%20message%20among%20other%20members%20of%20the%20force%20towards%20indiscipline.%20To%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20repetition%20of%20the%20same%2C%20retaining%20the%20constables%20in%20the%20force%20despite%20their%20failure%20to%20discharge%20their%20duty%20would%20be%20fatal%20for%20RPF.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20says%20Acharya%20is%20dismissed%20because%20he%20hid%20in%20the%20washroom%20of%20S-4%20coach%20instead%20of%20intervening.%20He%20saw%20Chaudhary%20removing%20the%20rifle%E2%80%99s%20safety%20catch%2C%20but%20left%20him%20alone%20with%20ASI%20Tikaram%20Meena%2C%20who%20was%20later%20killed%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20physically%20present%20at%20the%20time%20when%20Chaudhary%20took%20a%20passenger%20hostage%20at%20gunpoint%20in%20front%20of%20him%2C%20led%20him%20to%20another%20coach%2C%20and%20eventually%20killed%20him.%20Parmar%20too%20had%20hidden%20behind%20other%20passengers%20instead%20of%20intervening%2C%20the%20dismissal%20order%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Acharya%20is%20the%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Parmar%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20witnesses%20in%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaudhary%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20right%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20was%20moved%20to%20Akola%20prison%20after%20the%20RPF%20cited%20%E2%80%9Cthreat%20to%20his%20life%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20transfer.%20His%20lawyer%2C%20however%2C%20has%20moved%20an%20application%20seeking%20his%20transfer%20to%20a%20prison%20in%20Mumbai%20or%20neighbouring%20Thane%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710061503000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F10165435%2Fimage-1058.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftwo-rpf-constables-dismissed-in-train-hate-killings-case-for-failing-to-discharge-duties%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RPF%20constable%20Chetansinh%20Chaudhary%20was%20caught%20on%20camera%20hurling%20abuses%20at%20passengers%20from%20Muslim%20communities%20and%20gunning%20them%20down%20in%20July%20last%