4%C2%A0%20general%20and%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20an%20alliance%20has%20been%20sealed%2C%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20formally%20announced.%20The%20BJP%20said%20that%20the%20modalities%20will%20be%20deliberated%20in%20a%20day%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20reporters%20after%20the%20alliance%20was%20sealed%2C%20Naidu%20said%20that%20it%20will%20be%20a%20sweep%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20reported%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAndhra%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20destroyed%20badly.%20The%20BJP%20and%20the%20TDP%20coming%20together%20is%20a%20win-win%20situation%20for%20the%20country%20and%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20second%20round%20of%20talks%20between%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20BJP%20chief%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20Naidu%20and%20Jana%20Sena%20chief%20Pawan%20Kalyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fandhras-telugu-desam-party-pulls-out-of-modi-government%5C%22%3Epulled%20out%20of%20the%20NDA%3C%2Fa%3E%20(National%20Democratic%20Alliance)%20in%202018%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20grant%20special%20category%20status%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20TDP%20launched%20a%20%E2%80%98dharma%20poratam%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98fight%20for%20justice%E2%80%99%20and%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Ftdp-quits-nda-chandrababu-naidu-s-party-moves-no-confidence-motion-cong-and-left-to-support-move%2Fstory-zEOA5kDvoNU5GHs0yAfI1H.html%5C%22%3Emoved%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20NDA%20government.%20Labelling%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20a%20%E2%80%98terrorist%E2%80%99%2C%20Naidu%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofin