%2C%20those%20who%20were%20still%20trapped%20in%20the%20travails%20of%20this%20life%2C%20those%20who%20burned%20in%20the%20eternity%20of%20hell%20and%20those%20who%20sipped%20the%20nectar%20of%20immortality%20in%20the%20heavens%2C%20all%20became%20one%20and%20set%20their%20sights%20on%20Jhang.%20In%20their%20maddening%20rage%2C%20the%20apsaras%20of%20the%20court%20of%20Indra%20kicked%20around%20the%20mattresses%20and%20the%20pillows%2C%20trying%20so%20very%20hard%20to%20regain%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20court%2C%20of%20Indra%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20houris%20of%20Jannah%20were%20not%20faring%20that%20well%20either.%20Just%20a%20moment%20ago%2C%20they%20had%20been%20playing%20the%20%3Cem%3Edaf%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20drinking%20from%20golden%20goblets%20and%20singing%20heavenly%20songs.%20And%20now%20those%20seats%20had%20been%20abandoned%2C%20the%20juice%20from%20the%20golden%20goblets%20spilt%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20as%20all%20of%20heaven%20cast%20its%20eyes%20upon%20the%20Earth.%20Responding%20to%20the%20cries%20and%20laments%2C%20the%20monsoon%20wind%20rose%20like%20an%20army%20of%20soldiers%20from%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%20With%20lightning%20speed%2C%20as%20if%20it%20were%20the%20army%20of%20Hulagu%20Khan%20that%20had%20in%20time%20immemorial%20decapitated%20thousands%20of%20heads%20in%20Punjab%20and%20lit%20a%20bonfire%20of%20the%20heads%20to%20warm%20itself%2C%20it%20reached%20Jhang.%20Here%20these%20mercenary%20soldiers%20impregnated%20the%20clouds%20which%20blocked%20the%20view%20between%20heaven%20and%20earth%2C%20between%20its%20occupants%20and%20me.%20They%20unleashed%20a%20flurry%20of%20tears%2C%20crying%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20apsaras%20and%20houris%2C%20crying%20that%20a%20more%20beautiful%20creature%20now%20existed%20on%20earth%2C%20in%20Jhang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chenab%20was%20fuming%20with%20rage.%20As%20if%20intoxicated%2C%20she%20swirled%20like%20a%20bull%20in%20heat.%20She%20had%20to%20see%20for%20herself%2C%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20rumours%20were%20true.%20Daughter%20of%20the%20great%20Himalayas%2C%20the%20home%20of%20Shiva%2C%20the%20ascetic%2C%20the%20ultimate%20%3Cem%3Ejogi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20she%20had%20been%20hearing%20stories%20through%20her%20long%20arduous%20journey%2C%20in%20search%20of%20her%20lover%2C%20whom%20she%20had%20promised%20to%20meet%20at%20the%20Sindh%20coast.%20She%20raced%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Jhang.%20Oblivious%20to%20the%20pain%20of%20separation%20that%20her%20lover%20experienced%20in%20her%20absence%2C%20she%20headed%20off%20now%20in%20a%20different%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20310px)%2085vw%2C%20310px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08174651%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-08-at-5.46.21-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22310%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08174651%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-08-at-5.46.21-PM.png%20313w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08174651%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-08-at-5.46.21-PM-194x300.png%20194w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700820%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22479%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECover%20photo%20of%20From%20Waris%20to%20Heer%3A%20A%20Novel%20of%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20reaching%20her%20destination%2C%20finally%20reaching%20Jhang%2C%20she%20prostrated%20outside%20its%20tall%20towers%2C%20its%20tall%20buildings%20and%20its%20tall%20mound.%20She%20pleaded%20and%20begged%20for%20just%20one%20sight%20of%20her%20Heer%2C%20for%20whom%20she%20had%20broken%20her%20journey%2C%20for%20whom%20she%20had%20delayed%20her%20union.%20Like%20an%20invading%20force%20of%20Afghans%20marching%20into%20Punjab%2C%20she%20had%20progressed%20uninterrupted%2C%20until%20she%20had%20reached%20Jhang%2C%20the%20crown%20jewel%20of%20all%20cities%2C%20glorious%20as%20Lahore%20was%20once.%20If%20only%20someone%20had%20stopped%20the%20Afghans%20the%20way%20Jhang%20halted%20her%20journey%2C%20the%20way%20Jhang%20humbled%20her.%20She%20had%20come%20not%20as%20a%20conqueror%20but%20as%20a%20beggar%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20father%2C%20the%20most%20kind-hearted%20man%2C%20sire%20to%20the%20most%20beautiful%20girl%20in%20the%20world%2C%20could%20not%20ignore%20her%20wishes.%20He%20took%20Chenab%E2%80%99s%20hand%20in%20his%20own%2C%20placed%20a%20little%20flood%20water%20in%20the%20palm%20of%20his%20hand%20and%20poured%20it%20over%20my%20forehead%2C%20as%20if%20this%20was%20not%20the%20water%20of%20the%20Chenab%20but%20of%20the%20Ganga%20or%20the%20Abe%20Zamzam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20caressed%20my%20face%20and%20ran%20her%20fingers%20through%20my%20hair.%20She%20was%20assured%20that%20the%20rumours%20were%20true.%20That%20I%20was%20indeed%20the%20most%20beautiful%20girl%20ever%20to%20be%20born%20in%20Punjab.%20For%20if%20there%20is%20a%20river%20that%20knows%20beauty%2C%20then%20it%20is%20indeed%20the%20Chenab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20fateful%20night%2C%20as%20she%20held%20my%20face%20in%20her%20hands%2C%20she%20saw%20before%20her%20eyes%20the%20unfolding%20of%20my%20complete%20life.%20She%20had%20already%20become%20a%20participant%20in%20the%20love%20story%20of%20Punjab.%20She%20changed%20her%20direction%20permanently%20that%20day%20so%20that%20she%20could%20see%20for%20herself%20this%20immortal%20love%20legend%20that%20was%20to%20unfold%20on%20her%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlowers%20bloomed%20on%20the%20land%20that%20had%20been%20blessed%20by%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20Himalayas%20as%20she%20receded%20to%20continue%20towards%20her%20beloved.%20All%20these%20flowers%20faced%20Jhang%2C%20for%20they%20too%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20most%20beautiful%20thing%20there%20was%20to%20see.%20These%20flowers%20did%20not%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20spring%20to%20come.%20They%20smiled%2C%20sang%20and%20danced%20in%20the%20breeze%20and%20celebrated%20%3Cem%3Ebasant%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20day%20I%20stepped%20on%20the%20ground.%20The%20trees%20turned%20greener%20and%20their%20shadows%20became%20darker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssured%20by%20my%20laughter%2C%20the%20sun%20rose%20from%20the%20east.%20Throughout%20the%20day%2C%20it%20travelled%20through%20the%20sky%20to%20catch%20a%20glimpse%20of%20me%20from%20different%20angles.%20The%20moon%20existed%20to%20guard%20me.%20All%20night%20long%2C%20it%20kept%20the%20world%20illuminated%2C%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20anything%20or%20anyone%20who%20could%20threaten%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20spent%20many%20nights%20with%20the%20moon%20in%20its%20loneliness.%20I%20had%20lent%20it%20my%20ear%20to%20hear%20its%20tale%20of%20woe.%20Sometimes%20when%20it%20had%20cried%20to%20its%20heart%E2%80%99s%20content%2C%20it%20stared%20back%20at%20me%20with%20enquiring%20eyes%2C%20urging%20me%20to%20share%20with%20its%20lonely%20heart%20some%20stories%20of%20my%20misery.%20I%20had%20nothing%20to%20share%2C%20nothing%20to%20cry%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20with%20the%20moon%2C%20I%20did%20not%20have%20the%20heart%20to%20tell%20it%20that%20I%20had%20no%20complaints%20in%20the%20house%20of%20Chuchak.%20I%20could%20never%20summon%20up%20the%20courage%20to%20tell%20it%20that%20I%20did%20not%20need%20any%20protection.%20I%20did%20not%20tell%20the%20moon%20the%20tales%20of%20my%20fierce%20character%2C%20of%20my%20bravery.%20I%20had%20waged%20wars%20and%20led%20armies%20in%20the%3Cem%3E%20qissa%3C%2Fem%3E%20penned%20by%20Damodar.%20That%20battle%20is%20not%20part%20of%20this%20qissa%20so%20I%20will%20not%20delve%20into%20it%20any%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20fight%20armies%20in%20this%20qissa%20being%20penned%20by%20our%20Waris%2C%20I%20still%20retain%20my%20valour.%20I%20am%20a%20symbol%20of%20beauty%20and%20pride%2C%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20that%20I%20am%20also%20a%20metaphor%20for%20rebellion%2C%20for%20action%20and%20agency.%20Our%20Ranjha%20might%20be%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20divine%2C%20but%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20divine%20if%20there%20is%20no%20devotee%3F%20Would%20the%20divine%20be%20able%20to%20retain%20its%20divinity%2C%20if%20that%20divinity%20is%20not%20recognised%2C%20not%20worshipped%3F%20The%20divine%20is%20an%20object%20of%20worship%20and%20without%20being%20worshipped%2C%20it%20is%20nothing%20but%20an%20object.%20It%20is%20through%20the%20finite%20nature%20of%20the%20devotee%20that%20the%20infinity%20of%20the%20divine%20is%20recognised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20devotee%20is%20not%20a%20helpless%2C%20passive%20partner%20in%20this%20relationship%2C%20but%20rather%20the%20agent%2C%20the%20shaper%20of%20events%2C%20who%20makes%20this%20relationship%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20be%20mistaken.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20story%20of%20Heer%E2%80%93Ranjha%20but%20rather%20the%20story%20of%20Heer%20%E2%80%94%20Waris%E2%80%99s%20Heer%2C%20from%20Waris%20to%20Heer.%20You%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20see%20the%20parallels%20between%20Ranjha%20and%20our%20poet%2C%20our%20creator%2C%20our%20Waris%2C%20but%20it%20is%20really%20I%20who%20truly%20represent%20him.%20It%20is%20in%20my%20voice%20that%20the%20devotees%20speak%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Shah%20Hussain%20to%20Bulleh%20Shah%2C%20and%20now%20Waris.%20Sometimes%20I%20take%20the%20form%20of%20Radha%2C%20sometimes%20that%20of%20a%20nameless%20housewife%2C%20but%20it%20is%20always%20I%2C%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20it%20all%2C%20who%20become%20the%20symbol%20of%20a%20Sufi%2C%20a%20devotee%2C%20while%20Ranjha%20becomes%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20divine.%20I%20make%20possible%20the%20union%20between%20the%20devotee%20and%20the%20divine%2C%20the%20disintegration%20of%20the%20male%20in%20my%20female%20body.%20For%20neither%20is%20there%20a%20distinction%20between%20a%20devotee%20and%20the%20divine%2C%20nor%20is%20there%20any%20distinction%20between%20the%20male%20and%20the%20female.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20Waris%20and%20Waris%20is%20Heer.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709987386000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F08180545%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-08-at-6.04.56-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-excerpt-the-immortal-legend-of-wariss-heer%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20had%20spent%20many%20nights%20with%20the%20moon%20in%20its%20loneliness.%20I%20had%20lent%20it%20my%20ear%20to%20hear%20its%20tale%20of%20woe.%20Sometimes%20when%20it%20had%20cried%20to%20its%20heart%E2%80%99s%20content%2C%20it%20stared%20back%20at%20me%20with%20enquiring%20eyes%2C%20urging%20me%20to%20share%20with%20its%20lonely%20heart%20some%20stories%20of%20my%20misery.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-excerpt-the-immortal-legend-of-wariss-heer%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%3A%20National%20Conference%E2%80%99s%20Decision%20to%20Contest%203%20Lok%20Sabha%20Seats%20Exposes%20Fissures%20Within%20INDIA%20Bloc%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11163902%2Fomar-mehbooba.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20National%20Conference%E2%80%99s%20(NC)%20decision%20to%20contest%20from%20three%20out%20of%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Kashmir%20has%20irked%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20its%20Gupkar%20alliance%20constituent%2C%20raising%20clouds%20of%20uncertainty%20over%20the%20fate%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cunified%20fight%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20PDP%2C%20which%20has%20suffered%20a%20series%20of%20desertions%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20is%20reportedly%20eager%20to%20contest%20the%20upcoming%20election%20from%20the%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20seat%2C%20the%20home%20turf%20of%20party%20chief%20Mehbooba%20Mufti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20that%20his%20party%20would%20contest%20all%20three%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Kashmir%20has%20exposed%20the%20fissures%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20with%20the%20PDP%20chief%20also%20suggesting%20that%20her%20party%20might%20go%20solo%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20reporters%20in%20Srinagar%20on%20Friday%20(March%209)%2C%20Abdullah%20said%20that%20his%20party%20has%20conveyed%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20heads%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20much%20scope%E2%80%9D%20for%20negotiations%20(with%20the%20PDP)%20on%20seat%20sharing%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20out%20the%20PDP.%20The%20situation%20has%20kept%20the%20party%20out%20of%20this%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20told%20the%20(INDIA)%20alliance%20that%20our%20doors%20are%20open%20(for%20seat%20sharing%20with%20the%20PDP)%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20but%20that%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20they%20behave%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20query%20that%20the%20PDP%20was%20eager%20to%20put%20up%20its%20candidate%20on%20the%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20parliamentary%20seat%2C%20Abdullah%20said%20that%20it%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Cillogical%E2%80%9D%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhich%20(brand%20of)%20politics%20says%20that%20the%20parties%20which%20stood%20at%20number%20one%20and%20number%20two%20in%20the%20last%20parliamentary%20election%20should%20cede%20the%20contest%20to%20a%20party%20which%20was%20at%20number%20three%2C%20and%20that%20too%20on%20a%20seat%20where%20their%20influence%20is%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENC%E2%80%99s%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%20is%20the%20sitting%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%20from%20the%20Anantnag%20parliamentary%20seat%20that%20was%20rearranged%20to%20include%20Rajouri%20and%20most%20areas%20of%20the%20Poonch%20district%20across%20Pir%20Panjal%20in%20Jammu%2C%20following%20the%202022%20delimitation%20exercise%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20won%20the%20Anantnag%20seat%20(in%20the%202019%20polls)%20and%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20the%20second%20spot%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abdullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20coercing%20anyone.%20If%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20or%20Priyanka%20Gandhi-Vadra%20or%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20contest%20from%20there%2C%20we%20will%20happily%20vacate%20it%20without%20hesitation.%20But%20since%20we%20have%20won%20the%20seat%2C%20we%20will%20not%20leave%20it%20for%20any%20other%20party.%20It%20is%20our%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20displeasure%20at%20the%20tweets%20of%20Mehbooba%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20Iltija%20Mufti%2C%20without%20naming%20her%2C%20Abdullah%20said%20that%20the%20PDP%20leaders%2C%20despite%20being%20part%20of%20the%20Gupkar%20alliance%2C%20have%20targeted%20the%20NC%20more%20than%20they%20criticised%20the%20BJP%20during%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20annual%20Raising%20Day%20function%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20target%20the%20National%20Conference%20in%20their%20speeches%20and%20tweets%20and%20social%20media.%20We%20are%20now%20being%20dragged%20into%20the%20elections%20in%20Pakistan%20also.%20What%20kind%20of%20a%20coalition%20dharma%20is%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20joined%20hands%20with%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20to%20target%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20(NC%20president)%20and%20our%20party%20through%20Twitter%2C%20using%20the%20platform%20of%20the%20PDP.%20Maintaining%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20coalition%20is%20not%20only%20our%20responsibility.%20Unless%20those%20who%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20targeting%20NC%20mend%20their%20ways%2C%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20keep%20any%20big%20hopes%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20NC%20vice-president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20recent%20tweets%20by%20Iltija%2C%20who%20is%20also%20Mehbooba%E2%80%99s%20media%20advisor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20tweets%2C%20the%20PDP%20chief%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20without%20taking%20names%2C%20observed%20that%20the%20rigging%20in%20Pakistan%20elections%2C%20which%20has%20kept%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20party%20out%20of%20the%20government%2C%20had%20%E2%80%9Cuncanny%20similarities%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmass%20electoral%20fraud%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%201987%20assembly%20elections%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20historians%20and%20writers%20maintain%20that%20the%20NC%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20rigging%20of%20the%201987%20elections%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20which%20is%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20become%20a%20starting%20point%20for%20the%20full-blown%20armed%20insurgency%20that%20is%20in%20its%2035th%20year%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20tweet%2C%20Iltija%20posted%20a%20sarcastic%20emoji%20to%20mock%20the%20NC%20after%20former%20Union%20minister%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20claimed%20that%20the%20party%20was%20seeking%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20PMO%20only%20in%20night%20hours.%20Both%20these%20tweets%20were%20posted%20by%20Sarah%20Hayat%20Shah%2C%20an%20NC%20spokesperson%2C%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20after%20Omar%E2%80%99s%20media%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Omar%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D%20remarks%2C%20Mufti%20told%20reporters%20in%20Srinagar%20that%20she%20had%20earlier%20conveyed%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20leadership%20in%20New%20Delhi%20that%20the%20NC%20president%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctallest%20leader%E2%80%9D%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20who%20should%20take%20the%20final%20call%20on%20the%20seat-sharing%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20big%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20today%20and%20the%20announcement%20%5Bby%20Abdullah%5D%20is%20a%20serious%20setback%20to%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20cause%20and%20unity.%20What%20the%20government%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20do%2C%20a%20PAGD%20%5BPeople%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%20for%20Gupkar%20Declaration%5D%20member%20has%20unfortunately%20achieved%20it.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20has%20changed%20goalposts.%20Where%20we%20could%20come%20together%20to%20fight%20the%20bigger%20enemy%2C%20today%20we%20are%20face%20to%20face%20with%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20Gupkar%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20her%20party%20would%20pull%20out%20of%20the%20upcoming%20election%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccause%20of%20unity%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20PDP%20chief%20accused%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20making%20attempts%20to%20break%20the%20Gupkar%20alliance%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20it%20is%20the%20face%20of%20resistance%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%9D%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20PDP%20may%20be%20down%20but%20we%20are%20not%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mufti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20take%20our%20case%20to%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20let%20them%20decide.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20take%20the%20voice%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20to%20the%20parliament%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20voices%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20will%20be%20watched%20in%20the%20parliament%20by%20not%20just%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20but%20more%20than%2020%20crore%20Muslims%20whose%20houses%20and%20mosques%20are%20being%20demolished%2C%20and%20over%2080%20crore%20Hindus%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20PDP%20would%20make%20the%20announcement%20on%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20after%20consultations%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709986052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22htt