0Rs%206%2C000%20and%20online%20is%20Rs%2011%2C000.%20There%20is%20more%20demand%20for%20high-end%20phones%20online%2C%20say%20the%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20further%20share%20that%20they%20sell%20between%2055%2C000%20to%2065%2C000%20phones%20every%20month%20and%20have%20sold%20over%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263287%2Fbangalore-global-childrens-peace-award-photograph-kids-mobile-parents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%201.75%20million%20phones%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20date.%20They%20claim%20that%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20profitable%20from%20the%20outset%20and%20have%20achieved%20a%20consistent%20100%20percent%20year-on-year%20growth.%20Their%20revenue%20reached%20Rs%20187%20crore%20last%20year%20and%20is%20projected%20to%20hit%20Rs%20240%20crore%20this%20year.%20Operating%20in%20over%20100%20cities%2C%20they%20have%20a%20network%20of%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20difference%20between%20a%20second-hand%20and%20refurbished%20phone%2C%20explains%20Saket%2C%20is%20the%20quality%20and%20credibility.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20quality%20testing%20or%20checking%20done%20on%20a%20second-hand%20phone.%20We%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20problem%20with%20the%20phone%20and%20give%20you%20a%20warranty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20phones%20are%20also%20beneficial%20for%20the%20environment%20as%20they%20extend%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252476%2Fmumbai-e-waste-recycling-discard-dead-laptops-mobile-phones-computer-keyboard-ecoreco-book-my-junk-environment-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elifespan%20of%20gadgets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20prevent%20them%20from%20contributing%20to%20waste.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20Waste%20Electrical%20and%20Electronic%20Equipment%20(WEEE)%20forum%20reported%20that%205.3%20billion%20mobile%20phones%20wou